{"tid":1667001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民進黨：今天港府可以逼陳同佳到台灣自首 未來就可以逼港人到大陸自首","createTime":"2019-10-21T08:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:57:03.000Z","uid":144372,"like":959,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c9c79ebf22b7861b9380c7bd0476c361abb879","tid":1667001,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:23:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E6%99%82%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%A5-%E5%8F%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%80%83%E9%87%8F-062800320.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25A9%259F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25A6%25A5-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E8%2580%2583%25E9%2587%258F-062800320.html&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=baffe070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%8C%87%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E6%99%82%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E5%A6%A5-%E5%8F%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80-%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%80%83%E9%87%8F-062800320.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】台灣殺人案疑犯陳同佳遭台作出入境管制，台灣的國家安全局長邱國正表示，過去法務部、陸委會曾要求移送陳同佳，但未獲港府回應，認為港府現在卻突然要移送，時機不妥，台灣方面不得不在政治方面考量。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的立法院外交及國防委員會今日審查明年度國安局預算，期間有立委關注陳同佳案的後續。國民黨立委江啟臣在質詢時表示，「照這樣下去往後殺人都到台灣就好了，只要傷害的不是台灣人，台灣就不用在乎」，質疑台灣的司法正義、司法管轄權在哪裡。<br />\n<br />\n江啟臣指出，台灣方面應完整行使司法主權，此案若不處理好，大家會認為台灣的司法不是司法，政治干預司法、行政凌駕司法，以後來台灣犯罪只要把政治搞好，就不會被抓回來判刑，促國安局要慎重考量。<br />\n<br />\n民進黨立委羅致政則指出，若今天港府可以逼陳同佳到台灣自首或投案，未來就可以逼港人到大陸自首或投案，還不用修例逃犯條例。<br />\n<br />\n列席的邱國正答詢時認同羅致政的言論，認為港府提出的時機點很不妥。去年2月案發後，據他了解，法務部與陸委會都有要求香港將陳同佳移台灣，惟香港方面都沒有回應，現時突然要將陳同佳移送台灣，「在這個節骨眼上，政府不得不在政治方面也要作考量」。不過他同時表明，若果陳同佳入境台灣，便會立即進行拘捕。"},{"pid":"6b9732ec69037d11fc954cc380b931f66d5498bb","tid":1667001,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:24:06.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41558b6d803fe7b669da17beb687b99662f2fca4","tid":1667001,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2c250d835e7a715cc647d46da5f041f9723e80b0","tid":1667001,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74ede90c91e146f4c03c808dd8446c089b0d899","tid":1667001,"uid":91087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39845c2554b0923d312dbb6b4789e74fa7b0c500","tid":1667001,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4446945e2c51c3a06b762bb57e7da1158ec92c4","tid":1667001,"uid":250508,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"企硬呀台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0afec031bbf005fd3a9ac1fee60b35aab11414","tid":1667001,"uid":324668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\